---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="FAQ - OpenVila Astro Demo">
  <section>
    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <p><strong>How to get started?</strong><br />Run <code>openvila init</code>, <code>openvila scan</code>, and <code>openvila run</code>.</p>
    <p><strong>Can users define actions?</strong><br />No. Only owner-created actions can be executed.</p>
    <p><strong>Can scan include database content?</strong><br />Yes, if database sources are configured or auto-discovered.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
